            "description": "This example payload represents a collection of ledger records retrieved by the getAllLedgersByPayload function, each containing key details such as ledgerName and ledgerId. It illustrates how multiple ledgers related to Vision Foods are identified and listed for further processing within the Ledger Search business object.",
            "query": [
